Syntax (blueprint / recipe)

body {
	background-color: #f67280;
}

selector {
	property: value;
}

3 Selector Types:
Tag

#ID   /* start with hashtag */
.Class   /* start with period */

<h1 class="">
<h1 id="">   /* can only be used ONCE per page */
			/* purpose: you want something to be unique, either for presentation or clarifying */
